[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說五無反復經",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "宋居士沮渠京聲譯",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，佛在舍衛國，與千二百五十比",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "丘俱。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有一梵志，從羅閱祇國來，聞舍衛國人慈孝順，奉經修道，敬事三尊，便到舍衛國。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a08_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見父子二人耕地，毒蛇螫殺其子，其父故耕不看其子，亦不啼哭。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "梵志問曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是誰兒？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a10_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」耕者答言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是我之子。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志問曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是卿之子，何不啼哭，故耕如故？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」其人答曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「人生有死，物成有敗，善者有報，惡者有對，憂愁不樂，啼哭懊惱，何益死者？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "卿今入城，吾家某處，願過語之：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『吾子已死，但持一人食來！",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」梵志自念：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a15_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是何人，而無反復，子死在地，情不憂愁，而反索食？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人不慈，無有是比！",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志入城，詣耕者家，見死兒母，即便說云：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「卿子已死，其父寄信，但持一人食來。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以不念子耶？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」兒母即為梵志說譬喻言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「兒來託生，我亦不喚，兒今自去，非我能留。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如行客，來過主人，客今自去，何能得留？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我之母子，亦復如是，去住進止，非我之力，隨其本行，不能得留，愁憂啼哭，何益死者？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復語其姊：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「卿弟已死，何不啼哭？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」姊為梵志說譬喻言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我之兄弟，譬如巧師，入山斫木縛作大栰，安置水中，卒遇大風，吹栰散失，隨水流去，前後分張，不相顧望；",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我弟亦爾，因緣和會，同一家生，隨命長短，生死無常，合會有離。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我弟命盡，隨其本行，不能得留，愁憂啼哭，何益死者？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復語其婦：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「卿夫已死，何不啼哭？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」婦為梵志說譬喻言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我之夫婦，譬如飛鳥，暮拪高樹，同共止宿，須臾之間，及明早起，各自飛去，行求飲食，有緣則合，無緣則離；",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我之夫婦，亦復如是，去住進止，非我之力，隨其本行，不能得留，愁憂啼哭，何益死者？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復語其奴：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大家已死，何不啼哭？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」奴為梵志說譬喻言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b07_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我之大家，因緣和會，我如犢子，隨逐大牛，人殺大牛，犢子在邊，不能救護大牛之命，憂愁不樂，啼哭懊惱，何益死者？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志聞之，心惑目冥，不識東西：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我聞此國孝順，奉事恭敬三尊，故從遠來欲得學問；",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既來到此，了無所益。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又問行人：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛在何許？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲往問之。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」行人答曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b13_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「近在祇桓精舍。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志即到佛所，稽首作禮，却住一面，憂愁低頭，默無言說。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛知其意，謂梵志曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何以低頭，憂愁不樂？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志白佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不果所願，違我本心，是故不樂！",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛問梵志：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有何所失，憂愁不樂？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我從羅閱祇國來，欲得學問；",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b18_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既來到此，見五無反復。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何等五無反復？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b19_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志曰：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我見父子二人耕地下種，子死在地，情不憂愁而反索食，居家大小亦無憂愁，是為大逆。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不然！",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如卿語。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此之五人最有反復。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知身無常，財非己有，往古聖人，不免斯患，況於凡夫？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大啼小哭，何益死者？",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間俗人，無數劫來，流轉生死，遷神不滅，死而復生，如車輪轉，無有休息，背死向生，非憂愁所逮。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志聞之，心開意解，更無憂慼：",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我聞佛說，如病得愈、如盲得視、如闇遇明。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是梵志即得道跡。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切死亡不足啼哭，欲為亡者請佛及僧，燒香供養、讀誦經典，能日日作禮，復至心供養三寶，最是為要。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573c02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是梵志，稽首作禮，受教而去。",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說五無反復經",
        "from": "T17n0751a_001:0573c04_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]